background_description: The scene features a sandy foreground with gentle ripples, leading to a weathered wooden fence composed of rough logs. Beyond the fence lies a field of tall, vibrant green dune grass. In the mid-ground, there are forested hills partially obscured by a soft mist or fog, which blends into a cloudy, overcast sky. The overall color palette includes warm sandy browns, various shades of green, muted grays and whites of the sky and mist, and desaturated grays of the wooden fence.
